 community reaps the educational benefits of diversity while preparing future generations of leaders for a global society message from john etchemendy stanford university provost commitment to graduate diversity gap 2.5 the provost's diversity action council brochure 2004 16 page pdf file diversity works is a portal to diversity resources around the university exploring stanford's diversity student community schools & degree programs events for prospective students grad diversity day spring preview day recruiting schedule financial support each school's diversity officer can answer questions about graduate studies in their school contact directories maps & directions stanford university all rights reserved stanford ca 94305 650 723 2300 terms of use copyright complaints
